trans-unit.source: Indicates that the implementing property will be registered at runtime through the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Contexts.Context.RegisterDynamicProperty*> method.
trans-unit.target: 指示将在运行时通过注册实现属性<xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Contexts.Context.RegisterDynamicProperty*>方法。</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Contexts.Context.RegisterDynamicProperty*>

trans-unit.source: Dynamic properties can contribute sinks that are notified when remoting calls start and finish.
trans-unit.target: 动态属性可参与时远程处理调用开始和完成通知的收件人。

trans-unit.source: Returns the message sink that will be notified of call start and finish events through the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Contexts.IDynamicMessageSink"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: 返回的消息接收器将接收通知调用开始和完成事件通过<xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Contexts.IDynamicMessageSink"></xref>接口。

trans-unit.source: A dynamic sink that exposes the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Contexts.IDynamicMessageSink"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: 公开的动态接收器<xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.Contexts.IDynamicMessageSink"></xref>接口。
